reviewText: I got ripped off with this Dvd , it doesn't work

I have been watching the series on TV5monde/USA. Too bad Amazon.com does not have the NTSC, Reg. 1 USA. I would buy in a heatbeat.
A very good, sometimes poignant, always funny insider's view on north-african arabs multi-generational families living in Paris suburbs. The new young generation born in france and the parents, some of whom are desperately trying to hold on old traditions and others struggling (hilariously often times, tragically others) to make sense of it all.
All in all, lovely.
Charmant!!!
